OL,3,CLandmark report quantifies carbon in
OL,4,CUK seabeds
OL,6,FITV News Science Correspondent Martin
OL,7,FStew followed scientists in Yorkshire
OL,8,Fwho map marine carbon stores
OL,10,FConservationists call for the better
OL,11,Fprotection of the UK's marine habitats
OL,12,Fas the capacity to store carbon under
OL,13,Fthe sea has been mapped for the first
OL,14,Ftime.
OL,16,FThe new "blue carbon" report estimates
OL,17,Fthe UK seabed could absorb up to 13
OL,18,Fmillion tonnes of carbon every year,
OL,19,Falmost three times more than the UK's
OL,20,Fforests, thought they cover much
OL,21,Fsmaller area than the sea.
