OL,3,CLandmark report quantifies carbon in
OL,4,CUK seabeds
OL,6,FThe report by the Scottish Association
OL,7,Ffor Marine Science (SAMS) on behalf of
OL,8,FWWF, The Wildlife Trusts and the RSPB
OL,9,Fis the first time a country has
OL,10,Festimated and mapped its marine carbon
OL,11,Fstores.
OL,13,FIt estimates there is 244 million
OL,14,Ftonnes of organic carbon locked up in
OL,15,F10 cm of seabed sediments and coastal
OL,16,Fhabitats such as saltmash, kelp and
OL,17,Fseagrass beds.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
