OL,11,FHowever, experts warn that disturbance
OL,12,Fto the seabed by humans activities
OL,13,Fsuch as bottom trawling with fishing
OL,14,Fgear and the installation of offshore
OL,15,Fenergy such as wind farms, could
OL,16,Frelease the stored carbon worsening
OL,17,Fclimate change.
