OL,6,FTom Brook, blue carbon specialist at
OL,7,FWWF-UK, said: "This project reveals
OL,8,Fhow critical our seas are in
OL,9,Fregulating the climate and underscores
OL,10,Fthe urgent need to protect and restore
OL,11,Four seabed habitats.
OL,13,F"While saltmarshes and kelp forests
OL,14,Fpunch above their weight in terms of
OL,15,Fcapturing carbon, the mud really is
OL,16,Fthe star here ` accumulating and
OL,17,Fstoring vast amounts on the seabed.
